{"tid":1296570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彩虹站訊號故障　觀塘綫行車時間需要額外10-15分鐘","createTime":"2019-07-08T11:55:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T13:26:35.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"32b2421b4908e8875a9a17f67892101ee103d35b","tid":1296570,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190708/large/1562586464_a02d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190708%2Flarge%2F1562586464_a02d.jpg&h=9512d7a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵於晚上7時許宣佈，由於彩虹站附近有訊號故障，觀塘綫列車駛經鑽石山站和九龍灣站路段時需要慢駛，觀塘綫來往黃埔站及調景嶺站的行車時間預計需要額外10-15分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n觀塘綫服務更改如下︰<br />\n<br />\n黃埔站 往返 九龍塘站 每6分鐘一班<br />\n九龍塘站 往返 觀塘站 有限度列車服務<br />\n觀塘站 往返 調景嶺站 每8分鐘一班"},{"pid":"c6762df6bf04ae6c6a6ca39cfe0db2dc18e30374","tid":1296570,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:55:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190708/59802356\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190708%2F59802356&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpc2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=83bb3217\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190708%2F59802356&h=0358c161\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190708/59802356</a>"},{"pid":"b1fee6e236f9996bc01b13bffb445fd6066429f4","tid":1296570,"uid":4942,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:56:58.000Z","msg":"九龍塘站 往返 觀塘站 有限度列車服務 &lt;&mdash;&mdash; 又誤導市民，根本呢段就無車，唔撚郁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea840061f07d5aa3cdc5ec540fa84d57f47683e","tid":1296570,"uid":52764,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:59:13.000Z"